                    <li>‚Ä¢ Student loans and debt worries</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Cost of living pressures</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Part-time work stress</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Future employment anxiety</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">üè† Social Challenges</h3>
                  <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Homesickness and isolation</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Difficulty making friends</li>
