              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-4">üö® Warning Signs to Watch For</h3>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Persistent feelings of sadness or hopelessness</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Loss of interest in activities you used to enjoy</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Significant changes in sleep patterns</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Appetite changes or weight fluctuations</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Difficulty concentrating or making decisions</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Increased substance use</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Social withdrawal from friends and family</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Thoughts of self-harm or suicide</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Panic attacks or severe anxiety</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Extreme mood swings</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">‚úÖ When to Seek Immediate Help</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <div class="bg-red-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">Emergency Situations:</h4>
                    <ul class="text-red-700 text-sm space-y-1">
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Thoughts of suicide or self-harm</li>
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Severe panic attacks</li>
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Complete inability to function</li>
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Substance abuse crisis</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-red-800 font-semibold mt-2">Call 999 or go to A&E</p>
                  </div>
                  
                  <div class="bg-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-2">Non-Emergency but Urgent:</h4>
                    <ul class="text-yellow-700 text-sm space-y-1">
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Persistent low mood for weeks</li>
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Significant anxiety affecting daily life</li>
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Sleep or appetite problems</li>
                      <li>‚Ä¢ Academic performance decline</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-yellow-800 font-semibold mt-2">Contact Samaritans or university support</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Self-Care Tips -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-6">Student Wellbeing Tips</h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              
              <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-3">üß† Mental Wellbeing</h3>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-2">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Practice mindfulness and meditation</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Maintain a regular sleep schedule</li>
