                  <li>‚Ä¢ Regular exercise (even light walking)</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Eat balanced, nutritious meals</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Stay hydrated throughout the day</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Limit alcohol and avoid drugs</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Get natural sunlight exposure</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Practice good hygiene routines</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Conclusion -->
